  "instructions": [
    "Grill the fillet of steak for 4 minutes per side at 180\u00180C (356\u001864\u000085F) to achieve medium-rare. ",
    "Slice the onion and red bell pepper into thin rings. ",
    "Mince the garlic cloves.",
    "Slice the Uruguayan chorizo into thin slices.",
    "Brush the brine solution onto the fillet of steak for added flavor.",
    "Cook the sliced onion and red bell pepper in olive oil until softened, add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Assemble the burger with the cooked fillet of steak, onion and red bell pepper mixture, chorizo slices and parsley.",
